REM *** LESSON 21: CIRCLE SPRITE ***
REM Circular Motion with Trigonometry

NEW
10 REM *** CIRCLE SPRITE ***
20 FOR I=832 TO 894:POKE I,255:NEXT I
30 POKE 2040,13:POKE 53287,7
40 POKE 53269,1
50 REM CENTER OF CIRCLE
60 CX=180:CY=130:R=50
70 A=0
80 REM CALCULATE POSITION
90 X=CX+R*COS(A)
100 Y=CY+R*SIN(A)
110 POKE 53248,X
120 POKE 53249,Y
130 A=A+0.1
140 IF A>6.28 THEN A=0
150 GOTO 80
